---
title: Sweet Potato Curry with Paneer, Peas and Nutty Brown Rice
description: There are so many flavours and textures to praise in this dish, you'll wish there was more of it! Tender sweet potatoes, creamy paneer and rich coconut milk are perfectly complemented by lime and cashews.
